name: Search ja.is
description:
ja.is is an Icelandic online phone catalogue that provides contact information for most people and organizations in Iceland.
This extension shows search results from ja.is in the gnome search overview.

To view search results from ja.is, type the prefix "ja " followed by your search string.

It should be noted that this extension is not connected to the organization JÃ¡ in any way.
